## Key Lombok + JPA Rules Learned

- Always use `@NoArgsConstructor` on JPA entities — Hibernate needs it to instantiate objects via reflection
- `@RequiredArgsConstructor` alone will cause `constructor already defined` errors with JPA
- Subclasses don't need `@NoArgsConstructor` if they inherit it from the parent — but adding it explicitly is safe